{"tid":1590063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要建議]929要人","createTime":"2019-09-23T14:18:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T18:57:33.000Z","uid":133728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7d83469e42990e9caab4c8a05ce49ad0d04cd7fc","tid":1590063,"uid":133728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:18:04.000Z","msg":"大家可唔可以connect埋維吾爾族同西藏一齊搞<br />\n特別係維吾爾族 最近有國際關注 連Trump都會出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國公安押解逾百名維吾爾族人到庫爾勒囚禁<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=363792&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D363792%26refer%3DShare&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obsorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=83288625\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D363792%26refer%3DShare&h=2ef84c11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=363792&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n澳洲外長佩恩對片段深感不安，又譴責中國對待新疆穆斯林的手法，澳洲一直呼籲中國停止任意拘留維吾爾族人。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國大會周二在紐約召開，<span style=\"color: red;\">據報美國總統特朗普可能在發言中會提及新疆問題</span>，副總統彭斯和國務卿蓬佩奧亦可能在大會期間一唱一和，美國甚至會召開新疆問題會議。<br />\n<br />\n因為剩係得香港人去集會唔夠 藏族 維吾爾族 同埋台灣 都係中共重點打壓既對象<br />\n更加重要既係 佢地抗爭既路比我地更加漫長 更加有經驗 佢地絕對可以幫到手 壯大聲勢<br />\n我相信佢地亦會肯幫手 因為929主題正正係對抗中共既極權威脅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有人有辦法contact到佢地 盡量幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef7d6b3493f16b1c8129ce5f51329603bcbfa8b","tid":1590063,"uid":213383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:18:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"5c79e246916847aad895ab53abad3ea8e7d0ec26","tid":1590063,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:18:41.000Z","msg":"［行動post］10.1 維港悼念活動 燭光晚會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1588919\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1588919</a><br />\n<br />\n10月1日<br />\n晚上8點<br />\n維港兩岸<br />\n讓燭光燃點維港<br />\n悼念新屋嶺 &amp; 太子831 &amp; 運動中被逼害人士<br />\n<br />\n平反新屋嶺 平反831<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/20D1hbK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F20D1hbK.jpg&h=06acf2a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人不會忘記<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e81156e77a8f7c642eb8fe4a3c2de107765049d","tid":1590063,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"3e72cbed0c83ff100444833b8cf1b5c8141214e6","tid":1590063,"uid":311198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:19:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"060fca051cec50e6d32194f7a1c02a34d1d4a6ad","tid":1590063,"uid":133728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:23:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e7ceef9d417af7509fb9f5d26145e1338e66a41","tid":1590063,"uid":133728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:23:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a47dad803a41b54f3e11f9f4c8af27c1fc15c955","tid":1590063,"uid":133728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:24:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c344a831a3d3cfae83795ac77f3da3173f3f20a","tid":1590063,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:17:58.000Z","msg":"【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/edBrFS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/edBrFS</a>"},{"pid":"afad046ce0af39afd60dc2d0598f8675c7207a89","tid":1590063,"uid":278786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T18:57:33.000Z","msg":"如何做到有一百萬人以上，對和理非而言，最重要是不用申請不反對通知書而且有合法途徑。否則乜文宣都無用。<br />\n有條橋，就是抄何妖，佢話921清潔香港不用申請不反對通知書，仲串到撤銷遊行申請。<br />\n咁佢無被人拉無人告，心理上就可以宣傳：我地9.29/10.1搞的都是清潔香港行動，沿香港島電車路主線，人人執垃圾。口號可以加「清除香港垃圾，路線只有一條」，大家brainstorm 一下。<br />\n<br />\n人流控制方面：<br />\n可以呼籲港島人在自己區清潔；<br />\n九龍東人在鰂魚涌的香港殯儀館（象徵送中）以東，新界東人在鰂魚涌以西;<br />\n九龍西人在中環遮打花園以西，新界西人在中環以東。中環同殯儀館兩個地點也較方便過海人士。<br />\n<br />\n另一個重點，係需要有號召力的人或機構呼籲，大肆宣傳，俾和理非感覺既合法又多人陪，咁就安心參加。<br />\n<br />\n宣傳時戴埋頭盔，講明無集會丶無遊行路線，各人自發清除垃圾，自行發揮。<br />\n<br />\n利申：和理非"}]}